it.baywaylabs.jumpersumo.twitter

Class TwitterListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.String,java.lang.Boolean,java.util.List<java.lang.String>>
      • it.baywaylabs.jumpersumo.twitter.TwitterListener

  • public class TwitterListener
extends android.os.AsyncTask<java.lang.String,java.lang.Boolean,java.util.List<java.lang.String>>
    This AsyncTask (Async Thread) is called by the main (PilotingActivity) every one minute.
    This thread find the last twitter mention (@User ... ) after "idLastTwit", extract commands list, send to Robot and after finish reply to mention with a Tweet.
    Created on 21/11/15.
    Author:
    Massimiliano Fiori [massimiliano.fiori@aol.it]
    See Also:
    AsyncTask, Shared Preferences, Twitter4j Library, PilotingActivity
